        Selling in Ellen Grove 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Ellen Grove is a modern estate suburb built around young family demand in Brisbane's outer western corridor. Here is what sellers need to know about timing, estate pricing and the buyer market in 2026.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Body -->
